（三）配对样本T检验
1. 具体代码
在变量Ini.pro中，两个水平之间的反应时间是否有显著差异?
```{r}
df.0 <- rio::import("./hebing.csv")%>%
  group_by(subject, sex, Group, Ini.pro, End.pro)%>%
  summarise(RT = mean(RT))
df.1 <- df.0 %>% 
  group_by(subject, Ini.pro)%>%
  summarise(RT = mean(RT))%>%
  mutate(Ini.pro = factor(Ini.pro))
df.1
```


```{r dependent t-test}
t.de.0 <- t.test(df.1$RT[df.1$Ini.pro == "H"], 
                 df.1$RT[df.1$Ini.pro == "L"], 
                 paired = T, alternative = "two.sided")
capture.output(t.de.0)

df.2 <- df.1 %>% pivot_wider(names_from = Ini.pro, values_from = RT)
t.de.2 <- t.test(df.2$H, df.2$L, paired = TRUE)

t.de.3 <- bruceR::TTEST(data = df.2, y = c("H", "L"), paired = TRUE)
```


